## Spawned skill outputs

If a spawned skill requires dispatch scope fields that Mission Control did not inject, return **`partial`** with `outputs.missingFields` naming the missing binding (for example `dispatchId`, `operationsDocsDirectory`) ‚Äî do not invent ids or read sibling dispatch folders to recover scope.

